	成都诰令司书丞: 500活力就可以换一个地灵精魄，你确定要兑换吗?
	- 兑换1个地灵精魄
		if PlayerManager.player.player_energy >= 500:
			do PlayerManager.player.update_energy(-500)
			do PlayerManager.player_item_inventory.add_item("地灵精魄")
